# MindMate – Stress Recognition Quiz Chatbot

## Objective

MindMate is an AI chatbot that helps users recognize common signs of stress through an interactive quiz. It provides educational guidance and promotes healthy coping strategies.

## Problem

Many college students experience stress but do not recognize the early warning signs until it begins affecting their well-being.

## Solution

MindMate asks users a series of stress-awareness questions and provides supportive feedback and practical wellness suggestions.

